txt.en: 'Lanterns light the way around our woodsy village. It is important to not let the fires burn out! If you are walking around, would you mind inspecting the lanterns to see if any are low? Please feel free to refill any low lanterns you find, my friend.'
When neighbours work together, the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads will shine bright as the beacons.
Lanterns can be found in the Rohan Eastfold Homesteads.\n\nYou should fill the lanterns.
